Downloaded Hadoop by referencing below article-
https://medium.com/@MinatoNamikaze02/installing-hadoop-on-macos-m1-m2-2023-d963abeab38e
 
NOTE: Hadoop cannot work with Java 11, hence manually installing adoptopenjdk8
 
Worked Command-
brew install --cask homebrew/cask-versions/adoptopenjdk8
 
Referred:
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/55834845/unable-to-install-java8-with-homebrew
 
